Class AbstractLsNodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jackrabbit.standalone.cli.info.AbstractLs

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LsCollectedNodes, LsNodes

    public abstract class AbstractLsNodes
extends AbstractLs
    List nodes.
    The following attributes will be used in order to customize the output:
    • pathKey
    • uuidKey
    • mixinKey
    • nodesSizeKey
    • propertiesSizeKey
    • referencesSizeKey
    • versionableKey
    • lockableKey
    • referenceableKey
    • lockedKey
    • hasLockKey
    • newKey
    • modifiedKey
